{"tid":1525970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[極重要］所有夢遊人士同我 Disable & Delete Google Timeline!!","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:52:10.000Z","uid":236171,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8e70002a13918b76731a971e27b3f78e3c9efb","tid":1525970,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:47:21.000Z","msg":"問過原來好多患有夢遊症嘅人都唔知 Google Maps 有 Timeline 呢個功能。佢會 Track 住你邊日去過邊度。最緊要嘅係熄咗 GPS 都 track 到！（因為會用埋 WiFi 等等嘅定位功能）<br />\n<br />\n而家政府認為夢遊症患者對管治不利，加以逼害。為免俾人發現你有夢遊症，請睇下自己有冇傻奸奸留低條尾俾人捉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點入去？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Maps --&gt; Menu --&gt; Your Timeline<br />\n(以下為網上圖片，不涉及自爆。請安心享用)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwGV7sB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwGV7sB.jpg&h=ab6abd41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊日幾點去過邊度，行路定搭車全部睇晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9HussK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9HussK.jpg&h=599e73a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點樣 Disable 同 Delete?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n入咗 Your Timeline 之後：<br />\nMenu （右上角）--&gt; Settings &amp; Privacy<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wj3tH0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWj3tH0C.jpg&h=0ad6eef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n碌都底，如果你見到 Location History 係 On 嘅話就熄咗佢，同埋 Delete Location History<ins></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUsFy9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUsFy9H.jpg&h=56fa50d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家萬事小心，夢境平安。<br />\n我哋瞓醒再相認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4270003c0d8ff5b0f075c9f7af852ae4b48d03a","tid":1525970,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64021c8789294935e4a3a63bdc9181bc517cb90a","tid":1525970,"uid":28280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af97ac180f2739475acff1bd0049332c1335585a","tid":1525970,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"自推 x 10"},{"pid":"811b34da3cbfd5e305a2258e5120068fa4cd7ea1","tid":1525970,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"自推 x 9"},{"pid":"71834a643436259198585ccec20f6ab053a7dca0","tid":1525970,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"自推 x 8"},{"pid":"74d5875eba3ccf1d30d09b443edf11cbbae691a1","tid":1525970,"uid":308749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce71b1fdfb32349bf138a450222143bb8ae86be8","tid":1525970,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EBV7z0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EBV7z0.jpg&h=04974a70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YmbZPOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmbZPOm.jpg&h=3895b2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E75zDGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE75zDGG.jpg&h=74538fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zSY5mH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zSY5mH.jpg&h=dc026972&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkJA7z2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn